### =========================================
### FieldTrack API — Complete Test Suite
### =========================================
### Usage: Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code
### Then click "Send Request" above each request
### =========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@contentType = application/json


### =========================================
### AUTH ENDPOINTS (Better Auth)
### =========================================

### Register new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-up/email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Budi Santoso",
  "email": "budi@company.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "budi@company.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

###

### Get current session
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/get-session

###

### Sign out
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-out


### =========================================
### MOBILE — ATTENDANCE
### =========================================

### Check-in (multipart/form-data)
### Note: Replace 'photo' with actual file path
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/attendances/check-in
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary
#
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="latitude"
#
# -6.2088
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="longitude"
#
# 106.8456
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="selfie.jpg"
# Content-Type: image/jpeg
#
# < ./test-photo.jpg
# ------FormBoundary--

###

### Check-out (multipart/form-data)
### Same structure as check-in above
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/attendances/check-out
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary
#
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="latitude"
#
# -6.2088
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="longitude"
#
# 106.8456
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="selfie.jpg"
# Content-Type: image/jpeg
#
# < ./test-photo.jpg
# ------FormBoundary--

###

### Get my attendance history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/attendances?page=1&limit=10

###

### Get my attendance history with date filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/attendances?page=1&limit=10&from=2026-04-01&to=2026-04-30


### =========================================
### MOBILE — FIELD REPORTS
### =========================================

### Create report (multipart/form-data)
### Note: Replace 'photo' with actual file path
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/reports
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary
#
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"
#
# technical
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"
#
# Alat berat mengalami kerusakan pada bagian hydraulic system
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="latitude"
#
# -6.2088
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="longitude"
#
# 106.8456
# ------FormBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="report.jpg"
# Content-Type: image/jpeg
#
# < ./test-photo.jpg
# ------FormBoundary--

###

### Get my reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/reports?page=1&limit=10

###

### Get my reports filtered by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/reports?page=1&limit=10&status=pending

###

### Get report detail (replace :id with actual UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/reports/REPLACE_WITH_REPORT_ID


### =========================================
### WEB — DASHBOARD
### =========================================

### Get dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/dashboard/summary


### =========================================
### WEB — ATTENDANCE
### =========================================

### Get all attendance records
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/attendances?page=1&limit=20

###

### Get attendance with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/attendances?page=1&limit=20&from=2026-04-01&to=2026-04-30&type=check_in

###

### Get attendance with department filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/attendances?page=1&limit=20&department=Engineering

###

### Get attendance recap (work hours calculation)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/attendances/recap?from=2026-04-01&to=2026-04-30

###

### Get attendance recap for specific user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/attendances/recap?from=2026-04-01&to=2026-04-30&userId=REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID

###

### Get attendance recap for department
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/attendances/recap?from=2026-04-01&to=2026-04-30&department=Engineering

###

### Get map points (today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/attendances/map-points

###

### Get map points for specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/attendances/map-points?date=2026-04-28


### =========================================
### WEB — FIELD REPORTS
### =========================================

### Get all reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/reports?page=1&limit=20

###

### Get reports filtered by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/reports?page=1&limit=20&status=pending

###

### Get reports filtered by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/reports?page=1&limit=20&category=technical

###

### Get report detail (replace :id with actual UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/reports/REPLACE_WITH_REPORT_ID

###

### Validate report — Approve
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/web/reports/REPLACE_WITH_REPORT_ID/validate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "approved",
  "notes": "Laporan diterima, terima kasih atas laporannya."
}

###

### Validate report — Reject
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/web/reports/REPLACE_WITH_REPORT_ID/validate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "rejected",
  "notes": "Laporan tidak sesuai dengan fakta di lapangan."
}

###

### Validate report — Need Revision
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/web/reports/REPLACE_WITH_REPORT_ID/validate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "need_revision",
  "notes": "Foto kurang jelas, mohon ambil ulang dari sudut berbeda."
}


### =========================================
### WEB — USER MANAGEMENT (Admin only)
### =========================================

### Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users?page=1&limit=20

###

### Get users filtered by role
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users?page=1&limit=20&role=employee

###

### Get users filtered by department
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users?page=1&limit=20&department=Engineering

###

### Search users by name or email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users?page=1&limit=20&search=budi

###

### Get user detail with stats (replace :id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users/REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID

###

### Create new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Citra Dewi",
  "email": "citra@company.com",
  "password": "TempPass123!",
  "role": "employee",
  "department": "Operations"
}

###

### Create manager user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Manager Andi",
  "email": "andi@company.com",
  "password": "TempPass123!",
  "role": "manager",
  "department": "Engineering"
}

###

### Create admin user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Admin System",
  "email": "admin@company.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123!",
  "role": "admin",
  "department": "IT"
}

###

### Update user role
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users/REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "role": "manager",
  "department": "Operations"
}

###

### Update user name
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/web/users/REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Budi Santoso Jr."
}
